description:
MARK OF THE BEAST has created their second limited-edition face mask (featuring over 250 corporate logo spoofs) which is on sale now.  Each mask measures approximately 11.5"" W x 5.5"" H and is one-size-fits-all for adults (has elastic straps). The shown graphics are full-color dye sublimated on a dual layer 100% polyester microfiber spandex mask that is super soft, stretchy, easy to breathe through and machine washable.  Each face mask is also reversible, with blank black on the backside. *NOTE: These are not FDA approved and are not medical grade. 😷

Each order receives complimentary MOTB stickers.  Orders ship out in approximately two weeks, and all sales are final.  Link in profile. 😷
